FBIS4-59604 "drnes094_j_94001" FBIS-NES-94-094 Daily Report 15 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Saudi Arabia Yemeni Oil Minister To Brief Officials on Crisis Yemeni Oil Minister To Brief Officials on Crisis EA1505173294 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network in English 1600 GMT 15 May 94 EA1505173294 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network English BFN [Text] Mr. Salih Abu-Bakr Bin-Husaynun, the minister of oil and mineral wealth, arrived in Riyadh last night in the framework of his tour of several Arab countries. Bin-Husaynun said in a statement upon his arrival, that he would inform the officials in Saudi Arabia on the details of the battles in Yemen and the eight-point initiative put forward by the politburo of the Yemeni Socialist Party to stop the fighting and resort to dialogue.
